#

Herb-Crusted Pork Tenderloin with Ratatouille and Garlic Mashed Potatoes

$25
650 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

PorkComfort FoodDinner

Description

A succulent pork tenderloin encrusted with aromatic herbs, served alongside a colorful ratatouille and creamy garlic mashed potatoes.

Ingredients

  • Pork Tenderloin: 1.5 pounds
  • Fresh Rosemary: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • Fresh Thyme: 1 tablespoon, chopped
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Zucchini: 1, diced
  • Bell Pepper: 1, diced
  • Eggplant: 1, diced
  • Tomatoes: 2, diced
  • Onion: 1, diced
  • Mashed Potatoes: 2 cups, prepared
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Cream: 1/4 cup
  • Parmesan Cheese: 1/4 cup, grated
